    public class TypedPageButton<T>
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.link.BookmarkablePageLink<T>
implements BootstrapButton<TypedPageButton<T>>, Activatable, Invertible
    Renders a stable button link which can be cached in a web browser and used at a later time. The button will be styled according to the given button type and size.

    // creates a big red button new TypedPageButton("componentId", Page.class, ButtonType.Danger).setSize(ButtonSize.Large);

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    miha
